  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个医疗检验数据流的流程图。核心是从DiagnosticEngine开始，经过LabAnalyzer处理，最后同步到EMR系统。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我注意到您提到LabAnalyzer，这个环节是单次分析还是有多轮处理？另外EMR_Sync是最终节点吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "实际上LabAnalyzer需要两次处理——第一次初筛，第二次复核。然后才到EMR_Sync。另外我们在最后还需要一个DiagnosticEngine做结果归档。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所以流程是：DiagnosticEngine → LabAnalyzer（初筛）→ LabAnalyzer（复核）→ EMR_Sync → DiagnosticEngine（归档）。一共五个节点，四个步骤，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这个顺序。两个LabAnalyzer虽然同名，但是处理阶段不同，要区分开。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "我已经把五个节点按顺序连接好了。第一个DiagnosticEngine启动检验请求，经过两个LabAnalyzer阶段，再到EMR_Sync完成数据同步，最后回到DiagnosticEngine归档。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才说错了——第一个节点应该是发出检验指令的DiagnosticEngine，但最后一个归档节点也是DiagnosticEngine，这样会不会让人混淆？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确实，两个DiagnosticEngine功能不同。需要我在标注上区分吗？比如一个叫'诊断引擎-发起'，一个叫'诊断引擎-归档'？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "不用改标注，保持统一名称就行。实际系统中就是同一个服务，只是调用时机不同。流程结构本身就能说明问题。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，那当前结构是：节点A（DiagnosticEngine）→ 节点B（LabAnalyzer）→ 节点C（LabAnalyzer）→ 节点D（EMR_Sync）→ 节点E（DiagnosticEngine）。所有连接都是单向顺序执行，没有分支。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，这个流程是严格的线性顺序，不需要分支。不过我想确认一下，两个LabAnalyzer之间的箭头方向没问题吧？数据是从初筛流向复核的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认无误，B到C的流向就是初筛到复核。整个流程图已经完整了：DiagnosticEngine发起，经过两轮LabAnalyzer分析，EMR_Sync同步，最后DiagnosticEngine归档。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
  ],
